<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَرَوَاهُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ عَوْفٍ عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
